Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.90,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today we're all watching the skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.60,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}When looking for a comet, we find a skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:27.18,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Solve the puzzle of the scattered cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:28.60,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
