Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:41.19,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryoji Amatsuchi (34)\NHostel Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.85,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Heihachi Mikami (43)\NGuest
